===Noun===
'''martingale'''
# a piece of [[harness]] used on a [[horse]] to keep it from raising its head above a desired point
#{{nautical}} a [[spar]], or piece of [[rigging]] that [[strengthen]]s the [[bowsprit]]
# a [[gambling]] [[strategy]] in which one [[double]]s the [[stake]] after each [[loss]]
